playstore_details.title: SIA Secure OTP
playstore_details.description:
SIA Secure OTP is a two-factor authentication App that adds a second layer of security while accessing SIA S.p.A. messaging application and web portal. This works by generating one-time passwords on your mobile device which can be used in conjunction with your account credentials to make your login nearly impossible to hack. It implements Time-based One-time Passwords (TOTP) as specified in RFC 6238.

Special features:
* Support for multiple accounts simultaneously, each with distinct OTP token
* Protect your OTP token with personal password
* Automatic secure configuration through scan of QR code with encrypted content
* Generate codes even in airplane mode

Steps to use:
* Enroll OTP token for your account by scanning the QR code provided by the SIA application/portal (or manually enter the seed)
* Define your private password to protect each OTP token
* At every access to the SIA application/portal, input your OTP token password in the App and get your OTP
* Then simply input the OTP generated into SIA application/portal

Supported products:
* SIAnet.XS Portal
* Smart Integrator Standard

Please contact us for any queries/feedbacks.
